Author: cottonvoile
Text: I feel this. I am eating sort of okay, not maintenance but not terribly low because I need to think. I work out. Physically, this could be much worse.  But damn, the mental load of thinking about eating, whats safe to eat, how many cals have I had today? And worse than that the thoughts and guilt after having eaten. Im so tired too. Its taking everything out of me.  I hope that today is a better day for both of us
